headline: KeyBank Supports the Boys & Girls Clubs of Buffalo With a $5,000 Donation for 2 Pack a Backpack School Supply Drive
summary: BUFFALO, NY / ACCESS Newswire / August 20, 2025 / KeyBank recently contributed $5,000 to the Boys & Girls Clubs of Buffalo in support of the annual "2 Pack A Backpack" school supply drive with WGRZ-TV. This initiative plays a vital role in helping ...
